# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NZBN API — New Zealand Business Number register
# Register at: portal.api.business.govt.nz
# Sign the MBIE API Access Agreement before requesting a key.
# Use your sandbox key during development; switch to the production key for
# live calls. The two keys are issued separately from the same portal.
# Never share or commit this key. See docs/decisions/MBIE/ for obligations.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
NZBN_SUBSCRIPTION_KEY=
